Before writing the code :
Make a firebase account
Add your project on firebase as follows:
Android Studio-> Your project-> Tools-> Firebase->
click on authenticating email and password ->set up firebase
->add dependency
Done.You can see your project in your firebase console.
open it
click on sign in method ->enable google sign in
Make sure google play services is installed in your android project as Tools->SDK Manager ->SDK Tools and update ->Install it
make sure google-services.json file is now present in Project->App
